00:01:11.260 --> 00:01:15.970
Did you take the drug? The one you bought at the gym?

00:01:17.540 --> 00:01:22.290
If you messed with Sae Bom, you're dead.

00:01:26.330 --> 00:01:28.840
It seems like there has been a misunderstanding.

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:31.350
Then open this door right now.

00:01:52.270 --> 00:01:53.820
Where is Sae Bom?

00:01:53.820 --> 00:01:56.180
Sae Bom!

00:01:56.180 --> 00:01:57.630
What?

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:02.650
Hyun, are you hungry, too?

00:02:02.650 --> 00:02:04.260
What?

00:02:17.210 --> 00:02:21.090
Well, I came here because I missed you.

00:02:21.090 --> 00:02:22.520
- Help me out.
- What?

00:02:22.520 --> 00:02:23.830
- I said help me out. Stand up.
- What?

00:02:23.830 --> 00:02:25.540
Come on, stand up.

00:02:26.320 --> 00:02:30.880
We are newlyweds so I missed her a lot.

00:02:34.660 --> 00:02:39.820
I mean, he worries about me even if he doesn't see me for a short while.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:46.190
You must... You must love her very much.

00:02:47.890 --> 00:02:49.570
Of course.

00:03:00.790 --> 00:03:03.840
What is it? Why?

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:05.410
Do you want some?

00:03:06.320 --> 00:03:08.900
He has so many interesting things. Look.

00:03:08.900 --> 00:03:11.650
He also has a lot of food.

00:03:11.650 --> 00:03:15.320
- Weren't there any problems?
- No.
[Happiness]

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:20.740
[Happiness]

00:03:21.750 --> 00:03:23.620
